  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants, OrderListener, PrinterStatusListener

    public class MainFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener, OrderListener, PrinterStatusListener
    Main dashboard for dealing with xml You can load an XML from the top bar Or you can load a whole folder of XMLs Display the list of orders. Allows you to select one or more orders to print/preview Displays the Printer Status Gives you access to the other windows Reprint Window Order Detail Window of a specific order Print Window Preview Window Configuration Window MainFrame does not hold any actual data. All actual data are delegated to other class like FileSession in the model package
